trans-unit.source: Adds or removes the parts in the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch"></xref> from the container and executes composition.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona ou remove as partes do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch"> </xref> do contêiner e executa a composição.

trans-unit.source: This method is the primary way of directly adding or removing parts from the container.
trans-unit.target: Esse método é a principal maneira de adicionar ou remover partes do contêiner de diretamente.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> will always maintain a stable, composed state.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>sempre mantém um estado estável, composto.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, calling Compose with an empty <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch> is never necessary to start composition.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, chamando Redigir com vazio <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch>nunca é necessária para iniciar a composição.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch>

trans-unit.source: Instead, call the Compose method whenever you need to make changes to the parts available to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.
trans-unit.target: Em vez disso, chame o método de redação sempre que precisar fazer alterações às partes disponíveis para <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch> can contain both parts to be added and parts to be removed.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch>pode conter partes a serem adicionados e partes a ser removido.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionBatch>

trans-unit.source: Recomposition will take place only once for each call to Compose.
trans-unit.target: Recomposition ocorrerá apenas uma vez para cada chamada de Compose.

trans-unit.source: Changes to the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref> to include during the composition.
trans-unit.target: Altera para o <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref> para serem incluídos durante a composição.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pela instância atual do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar `Dispose` quando terminar de usar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose` método deixa o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>em um estado inutilizável.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar `Dispose`, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>para o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>estava ocupando.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada `Dispose` antes de liberar sua última referência a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref> e, opcionalmente, libera os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para liberar recursos gerenciados e não gerenciados; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para liberar apenas recursos não gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of all exports that match the conditions in the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma coleção de todas as exportações que correspondem às condições do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Implementations should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and should not throw exceptions for cardinality-related mismatches.
trans-unit.target: Implementações não devem tratar incompatibilidades de cardinalidade como erros e não devem lançar exceções para incompatibilidades de cardinalidade.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the GetExportsCore method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> objects.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se a importação solicita exatamente uma exportação e o provedor tem nenhum exportações de correspondência ou em mais de um, o método GetExportsCore deve retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>objetos.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>

trans-unit.source: The object that defines the conditions of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"></xref> objects to get.
trans-unit.target: O objeto que define as condições do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"> </xref> objetos a obter.

trans-unit.source: The composition transaction to use, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> to disable transactional composition.
trans-unit.target: A transação de composição para usar, ou <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> para desabilitar a composição transacional.

trans-unit.source: A collection of all the objects in this object that match the conditions specified by definition.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de todos os objetos nesta que correspondem às condições especificadas pelo objeto definition .

trans-unit.target: O padrão é vazio <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.

trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref> foi descartado.

trans-unit.source: Releases the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Libera especificado <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"> </xref> de objeto o <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The behavior of this method may vary depending on the implementation of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider> that produced the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> instance.
trans-unit.target: O comportamento desse método pode variar dependendo da implementação do <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider>que produziu o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>instância.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: As a rule, non-shared exports should be detached from the container.
trans-unit.target: Como regra, exportações não compartilhado devem ser desanexadas do contêiner.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> will only release an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> if it comes from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> that was constructed under a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy> context.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>será apenas a versão um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>se se trata de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>que foi construída em uma <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy>contexto.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Release in this context means walking the dependency chain of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> objects, detaching references from the container and calling `Dispose` on the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects as needed.
trans-unit.target: Versão neste contexto significa percorrer a cadeia de dependência da <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>objetos, referências do contêiner e chamar a desanexação `Dispose` no <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objetos conforme necessário.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> was constructed under a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy> context the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> will do nothing, as the specified <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> may being used by other requestors.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>foi construído em uma <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy>contexto a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>não fará nada, como especificado <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>maio sendo usado por outros solicitantes.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>

trans-unit.source: Those will only be detached when the container is itself disposed.
trans-unit.target: Aqueles só serão desanexados quando o contêiner é descartado.
